These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, ambient, punk, pop
1. the fan of ambient is between the fan of punk and the fan of pop##2
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | house | pop | ambient | punk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | soy-milk | lemonade | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, fish, lizard, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the frog##2
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | frog | lizard | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
